    "Warren W. Wiersbe": "How did the Lord care for David `[char_David_Rut_4]` (chapters 27; 29\u201430) even though David `[char_David_Rut_4]` had made a poor decision in fleeing to Philistine land?\n7. Saul believed in the Lord\u2019s existence, but his faith lacked humility and obedience. Why are these essential qualities of real faith?\n7. What qualities of Jonathan would you like to develop?\n7. The priests who serve in the temple during the kingdom age will be from the family of Zadok (Ezek. 40:45\u201346; 43:19; 44:10\u201316)."
